 of Congress collections.\n"], "link": "https://www.loc.gov/collections/patriotic-melodies/articles-and-essays/marines-hymn/", "slug": "marines-hymn", "title": "Marines' Hymn", "url": "https://www.loc.gov/collections/patriotic-melodies/articles-and-essays/marines-hymn/"}, {"content": "articles-and-essays/my-country-tis-of-thee.html", "description": ["The story behind the song \"My Country 'Tis of Thee\" with references to Library of Congress collections.\n"], "link": "https://www.loc.gov/collections/patriotic-melodies/articles-and-essays/my-country-tis-of-thee/", "slug": "my-country-tis-of-thee", "title": "My Country 'Tis of Thee", "url": "https://www.loc.gov/collections/patriotic-melodies/articles-and-essays/my-country-tis-of-thee/"}, {"content": "articles-and-essays/of-thee-i-sing.html", "description": ["The story behind the song \"Of Thee I Sing\" with references to Library of Congress collections.\n"], "link": "https://www.loc.gov/collections/patriotic-melodies/articles-and-essays/of-thee-i-sing/", "slug": "of-thee-i-sing", "title": "Of Thee I Sing", "url": "https://www.loc.gov/collections/patriotic-melodies/articles-and-essays/of-thee-i-sing/"}, {"content": "articles-and-essays/over-there.html", "description": ["The story behind the song \"Over There\" with references to Library of Congress collections.\n"], "link": "https://www.loc.gov/collections/patriotic-melodies/articles-and-essays/over-there/", "slug": "over-there", "title": "Over There", "url": "https://www.loc.gov/collections/patriotic-melodies/articles-and-essays/over-there/"}, {"content": "articles-and-essays/semper-paratus.html", "description": ["The story behind the song \"Semper Paratus\" with references to Library of Congress collections.\n"], "link": "https://www.loc.gov/collections/patriotic-melodies/articles-and-essays/semper-paratus/", "slug": "semper-paratus", "title": "Semper Paratus", "url": "https://www.loc.gov/collections/patriotic-melodies/articles-and-essays/semper-paratus/"}, {"content