 "slug": "victory-at-sea", "title": "Victory at Sea", "url": "https://www.loc.gov/collections/patriotic-melodies/articles-and-essays/victory-at-sea/"}, {"content": "articles-and-essays/youre-a-grand-old-flag.html", "description": ["The story behind the song \"You're a Grand Old Flag\" with references to Library of Congress collections.\n"], "link": "https://www.loc.gov/collections/patriotic-melodies/articles-and-essays/youre-a-grand-old-flag/", "slug": "youre-a-grand-old-flag", "title": "You're a Grand Old Flag", "url": "https://www.loc.gov/collections/patriotic-melodies/articles-and-essays/youre-a-grand-old-flag/"}], "active": false, "content": "$children", "link": "https://www.loc.gov/collections/patriotic-melodies/articles-and-essays/", "pagination": "3 of 3", "results": [{"content": "articles-and-essays/america-the-beautiful.html", "description": ["The story behind the song \"America the Beautiful\" with references to Library of Congress collections.\n"], "link": "https://www.loc.gov/collections/patriotic-melodies/articles-and-essays/america-the-beautiful/", "slug": "america-the-beautiful", "title": "America the Beautiful", "url": "https://www.loc.gov/collections/patriotic-melodies/articles-and-essays/battle-hymn-of-the-republic/america-the-beautiful/?fo=json"}, {"content": "articles-and-essays/anchors-aweigh.html", "description": ["The story behind the song \"Anchors Aweigh\" with references to Library of Congress collections.\n"], "link": "https://www.loc.gov/collections/patriotic-melodies/articles-and-essays/anchors-aweigh/", "slug": "anchors-aweigh", "title": "Anchors Aweigh", "url": "https://www.loc.gov/collections/patriotic-melodies/articles-and-essays/battle-hymn-of-the-republic/anchors-aweigh/?fo=json"}, {"content": "articles-and-essays/army-goes-rolling-along.html", "description": ["The story behind the song \"The Army Goes Rolling Along\" with references to Library of Congress collections.\n"], "link": "https://www.loc.gov/collections/patriotic-melodies/articles-and-essays/army-goes-rolling-along/", "slug": "army-goes-rolling-along", "title": "The Army Goes Rolling Along", "url": "https://www.loc.gov/collections/patriotic-melodies/articles-and-essays/battle-hymn-of-the-republic/army-goes-rolling-along/?fo=json"}, {"content": "articles-and-essays/battle-hymn-of-the-republic.html", "description": ["The story behind the song \"Battle Hymn of the Republic\" with references to Library of Congress collections.\n"], "link": "https://www.loc.gov/collections/patriotic-melodies/articles-and-essays/battle-hymn-of-the-republic/", "slug": "battle-hymn-of-the-republic", "title": "Battle Hymn of the Republic", "url": "https://www.loc.gov/collections/patriotic-melodies/articles-and-essays/battle-hymn-of-the-republic/?fo=json"}, {"content": "articles-and-essays/columbia-gem-of-the-ocean.html", "description": ["The story behind the song \"Columbia the Gem of the Ocean\" with references to Library of Congress collections.\n"], "link": "https://www.loc.gov/collections/patriotic-melodies/articles-and-essays/columbia-gem-of-the-ocean/", "slug": "columbia-gem-of-the-ocean", "title": "Columbia the Gem of the Ocean", "url": "https://www.loc.gov/collections/patriotic-melodies/articles-and-essays/battle-hymn-of-the-republic/columbia-gem-of-the-ocean/?fo=json"}, {"content": "articles-and-essays/eternal-father-strong-to-save.html", "description": ["The story behind the song \"Eternal Father, Strong to Save\" with references to Library of Congress collections.\n"], "link": "https://www.loc.gov/collections/patriotic-melodies/articles-and-essays/eternal-father-strong-to-save/", "slug": "eternal-father-strong-to-save", "title": "Eternal Father, Strong to Save", "url": "https://www.loc.gov/collections/patriotic-melodies/articles-and-essays/battle-hymn-of-the-republic/eternal-father-strong-to-save/?fo=json"}, {"content": "articles-and-essays/fanfare-for-the-common-man.html", "description": ["The story behind the song \"Fanfare for the Common Man\"